      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7198487/" class="title-link">中国精神病人生存状况</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7198487"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/librelove/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u5566623-15.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/librelove/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">黄三三</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-11-19"
      class="main-meta">2014-11-19 10:18:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7198487_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我并没有看过这本书 因为买不到 前年我在精神病院实习 精神病院的现状已经好多了 因为大多数病人入院的时间都已经比较长 大家都穿着入院前自己家里带来的衣服 使那里看起来比较像一个上个世纪的场景 但还是很祥和 大家都彼此熟悉 下午可以打麻将 在院子里活动 也有人唱歌  最小...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7198487_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7198487_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










